    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🌡️ How to read — Thermals\n**Coolant** normal **88–105 °C**. 🚩 sustained **>110 °C**, or climbing and not recovering (especially in traffic / at idle). &nbsp; **Oil** fine to ~120 °C, brief 130 under load OK; 🚩 sustained **>135 °C**.\n\n_The real signal is the **trend**: running hotter than usual for the same kind of drive = early warning._"
      },
      "transparent": false
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Temperatures (coolant / oil / intake)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "project300k"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "postgres",
            "uid": "project300k"
          },
          "rawSql": "SELECT timestamp AS time, coolant_temp_c, oil_temp_c, intake_air_temp_c FROM thermals WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp) ORDER BY timestamp",
          "format": "time_series"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "celsius",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "coolant_temp_c"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "yellow",
                      "value": 105
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": 110
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.thresholdsStyle",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "dashed"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": true,
          "displayMode": "list"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      }
    },
